<TEI xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" xml:id="K_7098" type="Brief"><teiHeader><fileDesc><titleStmt><title>Società Generale di Credito Provinciale e Comunale an Alfred Escher, Florenz, Montag, 20. November 1871</title></titleStmt><publicationStmt><p>Digitale Briefedition Alfred Escher, Zürich: Alfred Escher-Stiftung.</p></publicationStmt><sourceDesc><msDesc><msIdentifier><institution>SBB Historic</institution><idno>VGB_GB_SBBGB01_014</idno></msIdentifier></msDesc></sourceDesc></fileDesc><profileDesc><textClass><keywords scheme="http://briefedition.alfred-escher.ch/keywords"><term>Bundesrat</term><term>Eisenbahnen Finanzierung</term><term>Gotthardbahn-Gesellschaft (GB)</term><term>Gotthardbahnprojekt</term></keywords></textClass><correspDesc><correspAction type="sent"><orgName type="addressee">Società Generale di Credito Provinciale e Comunale</orgName><persName key="Escher (vom Glas) Alfred" type="sender">Alfred Escher</persName><placeName>Florenz</placeName><date when="1871-11-20">20. November 1871</date></correspAction><correspAction type="received"><placeName>Zürich</placeName></correspAction><correspContext><ref type="previous" target="B8101"/><ref type="next" target="B7095"/><ref type="next-in-corresp" target="B7095"/><ref type="previous-in-corresp" target="B8101"/></correspContext></correspDesc></profileDesc></teiHeader><text><front>
      
        <p rend="left" xml:id="K_7098_p1"><hi rend="printed">
            <lb xml:id="p1-l1"/>SOCIETÀ GENERALE
        
<lb xml:id="p1-l2"/>DI
        
<lb xml:id="p1-l3"/>CREDITO PROVINCIALE E COMUNALE
        
    <lb xml:id="p1-l4"/>AUTORIZZATA CON <choice><abbr>R. D.</abbr><expan>Regio Decreto (königliches Dekret)</expan></choice> <date when="1869-09-01">1<hi rend="sup">o</hi> SETTEMBRE 1869</date> <lb xml:id="p1-l5"/>Sede, Via Cavour, <choice><abbr>N.</abbr><expan>Nummer</expan></choice> 11
        
<lb xml:id="p1-l6"/><choice><abbr>N.</abbr><expan>Nummer</expan></choice>
        
<lb xml:id="p1-l7"/>ALLEGATI</hi>
        </p>
      
      <div type="dateline">
        <p rend="right" xml:id="K_7098_p2"><hi rend="printed">
            <lb xml:id="p1-l8"/>
            <placeName key="Florenz (I)">Firenze</placeName>, il</hi>
          <date when="1871-11-20">20 <choice><abbr>Novemb<hi rend="sup">e</hi> </abbr><expan>Novembre (November)</expan></choice> <hi rend="printed">187</hi>1</date>.</p>
      </div>
      <div type="opener"><p rend="center" xml:id="K_7098_p3"><lb xml:id="p1-l9"/>Monsieur,</p> </div>
    </front><body>
      <p rend="indent" xml:id="K_7098_p4"><lb xml:id="p1-l10"/>Nous avons l'honneur de
        
<lb xml:id="p1-l11"/>vous confirmer nos <rs>lettres<ref type="letter" target="K_7091"/><ref type="letter" target="K_7092"/></rs> des <date when="1871-11-18">18</date> &amp; <date when="1871-11-18">18 <choice><abbr>cour<hi rend="sup">t</hi> </abbr><expan>courant (laufenden [Monats])</expan></choice></date>, &amp;
        
<lb xml:id="p1-l12"/>de vous informer par la présente, que nous
        
    <lb xml:id="p1-l13"/>avons fait <date when="1871-11-20">aujourd'hui</date> à <choice><abbr>Mess<hi rend="sup">rs</hi> </abbr><expan>Messieurs (Herren)</expan></choice>Marcuard &amp; <choice><abbr>C</abbr><expan>Compagnia / Compagnie / Company (Gesellschaft)</expan></choice> <lb xml:id="p1-l14"/>de <placeName key="Bern (Stadt)">Berne</placeName>, un nouvel envoi de:</p>
      <p rend="indent" xml:id="K_7098_p5"><lb xml:id="p1-l15"/>
        <hi rend="underline">
          <choice><abbr>₤</abbr><expan>Livre suisse / alter Franken</expan></choice> 40000 Rente <placeName key="Italien (Königreich)">italienne</placeName> 5%</hi>
      </p>
      <p rend="left" xml:id="K_7098_p6"><lb xml:id="p1-l16"/>en les chargeant d'en effectuer le dépôt pour
        
<lb xml:id="p1-l17"/>notre compte, près le Conseil fédéral Suisse,
        
<lb xml:id="p1-l18"/>à valoir sur la caution de 10% que nous avons
        
<lb xml:id="p1-l19"/>à fournir pour notre participation dans l'affaire
        
<lb xml:id="p1-l20"/>du <placeName key="St. Gotthard (Pass)">S<hi rend="sup">t</hi> Gothard</placeName>.</p>
    </body><back>
      <div type="closer">
        <p rend="indent" xml:id="K_7098_p7"><lb xml:id="p1-l21"/>Agréez, Monsieur, l'assurance de notre
        
<lb xml:id="p1-l22"/>considération très–distinguée</p>
      </div>
      <p rend="right" xml:id="K_7098_p8"><lb xml:id="p1-l23"/>
        <hi rend="printed">Per la Societá Generale
        
<lb xml:id="p1-l24"/>di Credito Provinciale Comunale
        
    <lb xml:id="p1-l25"/>L'<choice><abbr>Amm<hi rend="sup">e</hi> Delegato</abbr><expan>Amministratore Delegato (Verwaltungsdelegierter)</expan></choice> </hi>
      </p>
      <div type="signature">
        <p rend="right" xml:id="K_7098_p9"><lb xml:id="p1-l26"/>
<persName key="Guardini V.">V. Guardini</persName> </p>
      </div>
      <div type="opener">
        <p rend="left" xml:id="K_7098_p10"><lb xml:id="p1-l27"/>Monsieur Alfred Escher
        
<lb xml:id="p1-l28"/>Président du Comité du <placeName key="St. Gotthard (Pass)">S<hi rend="sup">t</hi> Gothard</placeName> </p>
        <p rend="indent" xml:id="K_7098_p11"><lb xml:id="p1-l29"/>
          <placeName key="Zürich (Stadt)">Zurich</placeName>.</p>
      </div>
    </back></text></TEI>